rse is positioned within the curriculum in accordance with the diploma policy and curriculum policy established by each undergraduate/graduate school. By proceeding with the study of this course with an awareness of the DP and CP, the following abilities expected by each undergraduate/graduate school will be developed.General Foundation Courses (Basic Courses):&nbsp;1. Understanding and analytical skills regarding international issues: the ability to understand and analyze various regions of the world from different perspectives in the humanities and social sciences."], "成績評価Grading0": ["種別　Type備考　Note", "割合　Percentage", "評価基準等　Grading Criteria etc."], "成績評価Grading1": ["授業中試験／In-class examination (03)", "40 %", ""], "成績評価Grading2": ["その他／Others (99)", "60 %", "First In-Class Test, Participation"], "成績評価Grading3": ["備考　Note Students will be expected to participate in class discussions and may be asked to complete small assignments from time to time. These will factor into the participation grade which is twenty-five percent of the final grade. There will be an in-class midterm test and an in-class exam. These will be worth 35% and 40% of the grade respectively."], "更新日時/Date of Update0": ["2026年01月19日 18時35分21秒"], "項番No.0": [], "項番No.1": ["2026年度", "春学期／Spring", "火曜２時限／Tuesday 2", "春学期／Spring", "Ｇ－ＩＳ１０４"]}, "campas": 0, "name": "【120】Introduction to International History／Introduction to International History [EN]", "管理部署": 10, "単位数": 2, "担当者": "ウォルシュ　Ｂ．（WALSH BRIAN） ", "履修基準年度": "１年", "履修登録方法": "本登録", "開講期": 1, "時限1": 8, "評価1": 2, "評価2": 6, "成績評価備考": "備考　Note\nStudents will be expected to participate in class discussions and may be asked to complete small assignments from time to time. These will factor into the participation grade which is twenty-five percent of the final grade. There will be an in-class midterm test and an in-class exam. These will be worth 35% and 40% of the grade respectively."}